<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-10-03T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-10-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="733" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d733">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 838.001 Au 4/2.]</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Minister of Haiti</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Translation]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Haiti</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-10-03">
                                    <hi rend="italic">October 3, 1912</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. Secretary of State</hi>: I have the honor of
                            transmitting to you accompanied by the customary copy, the autograph
                            letter, by which Mr. Tancrède Auguste informs the President of the
                            United States of America of his election to the Presidency of the
                            Republic of Haiti.</p>
                        <p>In begging you to kindly let this letter reach its high destination, I
                            renew [etc.]</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Solón Menos.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>